1 . Go to http://www-01.ibm.com/support/docview.wss?uid=swg2C4000051 and login

2. In the bottom of this webpage you got the downloading link 

3. Unzip this .zip file and move it to /opt folder 

4. open the unzipped dir and run the coomand
    ./install-server.sh
    
    make sure you have jdk installed with ENV variable
    
5. After installation go to /ibm-ucd/server/bin dir in the /opt folder 
and run a command ./server start

then check the connection on https://localhost:8443
   
